     1→# Alternative backends
     3→A "backend" is simply a program which `mdbook` will invoke during the book
     4→rendering process. This program is passed a JSON representation of the book and
     5→configuration information via `stdin`. Once the backend receives this
     6→information it is free to do whatever it wants.
