    42→## Search
    44→Each book has a built-in search system.
    45→Pressing the search icon <i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i> in the menu bar, or pressing the <kbd>/</kbd> or <kbd>S</kbd> key on the keyboard will open an input box for entering search terms.
